[
  {
    "text": "In a couple more hours this mud\nwill be perfect to play in!",
    "start": 0.083,
    "duration": 3.379
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey guys, why can't a comedian\ntell a dirty laundry joke?",
    "start": 4.046,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "'Cause it always comes out clean.",
    "start": 7.466,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 9.551,
    "duration": 0.709
  },
  {
    "text": "I bloody love this song!",
    "start": 10.344,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Sing it like you mean it, Mick!",
    "start": 12.638,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm trying to write here.",
    "start": 14.848,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I love you more, silly.",
    "start": 18.727,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "It's our six week-iversary.",
    "start": 21.146,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "You two are like, gonna be together\nfor like, ever.",
    "start": 22.773,
    "duration": 3.128
  },
  {
    "text": "Speaking of forever, Lori,",
    "start": 26.026,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "my study indicates you haven't\nused the bathroom in quite some time.",
    "start": 27.736,
    "duration": 3.962
  },
  {
    "text": "Ew! There is no way I'm being\nin your grody poop study.",
    "start": 31.823,
    "duration": 3.879
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah, rainy days.",
    "start": 35.786,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Perfect for hanging out with\nthe family and reading comics.",
    "start": 37.871,
    "duration": 3.337
  },
  {
    "text": "- Gross!\n- What?",
    "start": 44.503,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Why do you always have to read\nyour comics in your underpants?",
    "start": 46.755,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Because reading my comics with my clothes\non is uncomfortable and distracting.",
    "start": 49.174,
    "duration": 3.671
  },
  {
    "text": "And you know how I like to be\ncomfortable while reading comics.",
    "start": 52.97,
    "duration": 2.627
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now scooch.\n- Ah!",
    "start": 55.722,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "It's an annoying habit and\nyou get butt germs everywhere!",
    "start": 57.558,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Me annoying? You can't look away\nfrom the mirror for five seconds.",
    "start": 60.978,
    "duration": 4.004
  },
  {
    "text": "Lies!",
    "start": 65.065,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "And Lori, would it kill you not to\ntalk to Bobby all the time?",
    "start": 67.734,
    "duration": 3.963
  },
  {
    "text": "I do not talk to Bobby all the time.\nDo I, Bobby?",
    "start": 71.78,
    "duration": 3.462
  },
  {
    "text": "And Lisa, you always do\nyour weird poop studies.",
    "start": 75.325,
    "duration": 3.337
  },
  {
    "text": "It's quite fascinating work.",
    "start": 78.745,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "See? You guys couldn't last 10 minutes\nwithout doing your annoying things.",
    "start": 80.622,
    "duration": 4.004
  },
  {
    "text": "- We could last longer than you.\n- I bet you couldn't.",
    "start": 84.71,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, really?",
    "start": 88.13,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "Care to make it a little more interesting?",
    "start": 90.549,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "If we can stop doing our things\nlonger than you can stop doing yours,",
    "start": 93.635,
    "duration": 4.171
  },
  {
    "text": "then you have to give up\nreading in your underwear forever!",
    "start": 97.931,
    "duration": 4.421
  },
  {
    "text": "- Yeah!\n- Hold it.",
    "start": 102.436,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "What's in it for me?",
    "start": 104.646,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "If you win, we'll never complain\nabout your butt cooties again.",
    "start": 106.231,
    "duration": 3.837
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, but if I beat you,",
    "start": 110.152,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "you also have to buy me\nthese beauties.",
    "start": 112.404,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "Pure cotton, 2,000 thread count,",
    "start": 115.157,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "non-binding elastic.",
    "start": 117.826,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll just call them my victory undies.",
    "start": 120.078,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "[whispering]",
    "start": 123.123,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- Deal.\n- Great.",
    "start": 128.378,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "So if I have to read comics\nwith my clothes on,",
    "start": 129.796,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "Lola can't look in a mirror,\nLuna can't speak in a British accent,",
    "start": 132.257,
    "duration": 3.504
  },
  {
    "text": "- Lana can't play in the mud.\n- Dang it.",
    "start": 136.678,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- Lori can't talk to Bobby.\n- Bobby who?",
    "start": 139.097,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "- Leni can't say 'like'.\n- Like, OK.",
    "start": 141.892,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "Lucy can't pop up and scare people.",
    "start": 144.603,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "- Lisa has to give up her weird studies.\n- Forgive me, science.",
    "start": 147.356,
    "duration": 3.587
  },
  {
    "text": "Luan can't tell bad jokes.",
    "start": 151.026,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Lynn can't turn everything into a sport.",
    "start": 153.32,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "And Lily can't cry.",
    "start": 155.989,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "- Deal.\n- Pants up, buddy boy.",
    "start": 159.409,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, competition starts now.",
    "start": 162.079,
    "duration": 3.462
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait, like, I wasn't clear on the rules.",
    "start": 165.624,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "Leni, you can't say 'like'.",
    "start": 168.293,
    "duration": 3.212
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh, got it.\n- OK.",
    "start": 171.964,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "Competition starts now.",
    "start": 173.799,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm like totally gonna win this.",
    "start": 176.26,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "[buzzer]",
    "start": 178.053,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- Nice going.\n- Ah!",
    "start": 179.68,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "[buzzer]",
    "start": 181.64,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "Dang it.",
    "start": 182.808,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, ladies, stay focused!",
    "start": 183.892,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "Two down. I can practically\nsmell those victory undies.",
    "start": 186.562,
    "duration": 3.962
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait, let me rephrase that.",
    "start": 190.607,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "See? I don't even need a mirror\nto put my makeup on.",
    "start": 195.445,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "Comfy over there, Lincoln?",
    "start": 198.907,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep, just about to dive...",
    "start": 201.076,
    "duration": 4.129
  },
  {
    "text": "into my comics...",
    "start": 205.372,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "[groaning]",
    "start": 207.624,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "[phone ringing]",
    "start": 210.127,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "[moaning]",
    "start": 212.546,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Control yourself, woman!",
    "start": 214.673,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, nothing sporty\nabout folding laundry.",
    "start": 217.509,
    "duration": 3.087
  },
  {
    "text": "Or funny.",
    "start": 220.679,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "[panting]",
    "start": 228.228,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Lana, heal!",
    "start": 229.813,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "[whining]",
    "start": 231.773,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "[whining]",
    "start": 235.736,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Hairdy-verdy-verdy.\nEasy peasy.",
    "start": 237.404,
    "duration": 3.545
  },
  {
    "text": "I just switched to Swedish, ya.",
    "start": 241.074,
    "duration": 2.128
  },
  {
    "text": "You poor fragile homo sapiens.",
    "start": 243.785,
    "duration": 2.753
  },
  {
    "text": "[phone ringing]",
    "start": 246.622,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "- I will take that, ya.\n- No you von't!",
    "start": 247.789,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, won't!",
    "start": 250.125,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Gimme!",
