    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "Basketball...",
    "start": 256.965,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't do it! Don't do it!",
    "start": 259.343,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Two points! Two points! Two points!\nTwo points! Two points! Two points!",
