  {
    "text": "Plus, these are so comfy.",
    "start": 300.259,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Good luck. Those are the ones\nthat really ride up on ya.",
    "start": 302.344,
    "duration": 4.421
  },
  {
    "text": "Sure, Lori. You're just trying\nto mess with my-- Hello!",
    "start": 306.89,
    "duration": 3.754
  },
  {
    "text": "Yup, those are riding.",
